<h2>
    About</h2>
<p>
    Grid.Mvc adds functionality for creating GridView controls in your ASP.NET MVC 3
    web application. It is a component that allows you easy construction of HTML tables
    for displaying, paging, sorting and filtering data from a collection of Model objects.
</p>
<p>
    For more documentation, please see: <a href="http://gridmvc.codeplex.com/">http://gridmvc.codeplex.com/</a>
</p>
